  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO AUTHORIZE AN INCOME TAX CREDIT, INSURANCE PREMIUM TAX CREDIT AND AD VALOREM TAX CREDIT FOR VOLUNTARY CASH CONTRIBUTIONS BY CERTAIN TAXPAYERS TO CERTAIN ELIGIBLE HOSPITALS; TO PROVIDE THE CRITERIA THAT A HOSPITAL MUST MEET IN ORDER FOR A CONTRIBUTION TO THE HOSPITAL TO QUALIFY FOR THE TAX CREDIT AUTHORIZED BY THIS ACT; TO LIMIT THE AMOUNT OF THE CREDIT; TO PROVIDE THAT UNUSED PORTIONS OF A CREDIT MAY BE CARRIED FORWARD FOR FIVE CONSECUTIVE YEARS FROM THE CLOSE OF THE TAX YEAR IN WHICH THE CREDIT WAS EARNED; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
  },
